### RxDB Collection with Custom Conflict Handler (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/transactions-conflicts-revisions.html

Demonstrates how to specify a custom conflict handler when adding collections to an RxDB database. This allows for tailored conflict detection and resolution logic within your application.

```javascript
const myCollections = await myDatabase.addCollections({
